# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-maintenance
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document the long-term maintenance tasks required to keep the cluster
#   healthy, stable, and ready for distributed kernel builds.
#
# Maintenance Tasks:
#
#   1. Monthly
#      - Run cluster-health.yml
#      - Run cluster-filesystem-integrity.yml
#      - Run cluster-power-report.yml
#
#   2. Quarterly
#      - Verify distccd versions across nodes
#      - Rebuild kernel with updated toolchain
#      - Validate kernel config drift
#
#   3. After Every Kernel Deployment
#      - Run verification pipeline
#      - Check dmesg for warnings
#      - Confirm k3s workloads are stable
#
#   4. As Needed
#      - Replace SD cards showing corruption
#      - Rebalance DISTCC_HOSTS based on performance
#
# Notes:
#   - This file defines the authoritative maintenance schedule.
# =============================================================================
